üêë Program SheepCounter

Description:
The program counts sheep using a while loop and prints each sheep number.

Modification Questions
1. Change the program so counting starts at 3 instead of 1.
2. Make the program stop counting at 50 sheep instead of the current limit.
3. Modify the loop so only even numbers of sheep are printed.
4. Add a private variable to store the maximum number of sheep.
5. Change the loop so it counts downwards instead of upwards.

