Description:
You are going to work with a classic song program called Bottle Song.
The program counts down bottles of soda using a while loop and prints the song verses.
It uses OOP principles, with a class, a private variable, a constructor, and a method.
Expected Output:
3 bottles of soda on the wall, 3 bottles of soda!
Take one down, pass it around, 2 bottles of soda on the wall.

2 bottles of soda on the wall, 2 bottles of soda!
Take one down, pass it around, 1 bottles of soda on the wall.

1 bottles of soda on the wall, 1 bottles of soda!
Take one down, pass it around, 0 bottles of soda on the wall.

No more bottles of soda on the wall! üçæ